---
description: Geometry and animation IR test tiers — read before adding or changing IR-related tests
globs:
  - tests/**/*.cs
  - docs/generated/**
  - src/AutoPBR.Core/Data/minecraft-native/*geometry*
  - src/AutoPBR.Core/Data/minecraft-native/*animation*
---

When adding or changing geometry or animation IR tests, follow [docs/test-guidance-geometry-animation-ir.md](../../docs/test-guidance-geometry-animation-ir.md) and the canonical plan [docs/runtime-ir-preview-plan.md](../../docs/runtime-ir-preview-plan.md). For ghast-family files, also read [docs/ghast-family-parity.md](../../docs/ghast-family-parity.md).

- Default CI: T0 invariants + T1 pilot allowlists only.
- Do not assert strict goldens on `partial` / `heuristic` shards or whole-index counts without `AUTOPBR_RUN_LIFT_QUALITY_INDEX=1`.
- Promote models by editing allowlists under `src/AutoPBR.Core/Data/minecraft-native/` in the same PR as shard updates.
